01:45.192 --> 01:46.823
Oh, I should really stop watching QVC.

01:46.848 --> 01:49.266
- My finger.
- I'ma get you some ice.

01:50.998 --> 01:52.542
Hi, Maggie.

01:52.566 --> 01:54.680
Here's the air mattress
you asked to borrow.

01:54.705 --> 01:56.616
Thank you, Emily.

01:56.641 --> 01:58.100
Full disclosure:

01:58.125 --> 02:00.295
David and I bought it
for a fun camping trip,

02:00.320 --> 02:04.243
