and fall and hurt myself.

04:45.171 --> 04:46.577
Thank you.

04:46.602 --> 04:50.360
The crazy thing is, it actually works.

04:51.144 --> 04:52.643
I guess dads just have a way

04:52.668 --> 04:54.368
