08:32.948 --> 08:34.433
Hey.

08:38.841 --> 08:41.778
How'd it go with your dad last night?

08:42.042 --> 08:43.686
It was...

08:43.801 --> 08:46.198
emotional, but necessary.

08:46.223 --> 08:50.261
Thank you for encouraging me
to go over there and face him.

08:50.286 --> 08:51.723
Sure.

08:52.219 --> 08:55.974
