09:49.072 --> 09:52.755
just so I can get a sense
of how you're thinking

09:52.779 --> 09:55.791
about this whole crazy thing.

09:55.815 --> 09:57.760
Mm-hmm, mm-hmm, mm-hmm.

09:57.784 --> 10:00.594
